Get the Response Variable Units from a BayesPharma Model

get_response_units.Rd

Get the Response Variable Units from a BayesPharma Model

Usage

get_response_units(model)

Arguments

model

bpfit object resulting from fitting a model with one of the model functions from the BayesPharma package.

Value

character with the response variable units
